ropose that the 50 splice sites at intron 3 are weak, resulting in multiple alternative splicing events in intron 3 of female Lepidoptera dsx. Activation of the 50 splice site requires regulatory cis-elements in exons 3 for female-speciﬁc splicing of Lepidoptera dsx.},
